-- Topics: 5.3.1 through 5.7.1
-- Source basis: ISC2 CBK, NIST SP 800-63B (authentication), NIST SP 800-162 (ABAC),
--               NIST SP 800-207 (Zero Trust), RFC 4120 (Kerberos), RFC 6749 (OAuth 2.0),
